THE GAME
--------

  'E_vaz_ive' is a Workbench game where you have to move a
coloured hexagonal shape from the top of the game board to the
exit tile, located somewhere at the bottom of the board. To move,
you must follow the coloured links in order to go from one tile to
another. Also, to complete a game board, none of the small
hexagonal shapes that are located on the game tiles, including the
one on the exit tile, must be either in black or white (or whatever
colours you use as colour 1 and 2 in the Workbench palette).

  When you go from one tile to another, the shape that is located
on the previous tile will change its colour. If you return to that
tile and go on another tile, the shape of the tile will again
change colour (as well as that of the other tile) and so on...
eventually, it will return to its original colour.

  When you complete a game board, E_vaz_ive will display a new
game board and the game will continue...

  As usual, the least amount of moves you make to complete a game
board, the better it is...

  Have fun!

